      "date": "2011-11-22 20:15:06.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.7/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/66fe00a4-1544-11e1-b669-52540025f9af).  Ran 15 tests.  1 tests failed: replay-dual.",
